HEADWORD: Towboat
<hw>Tow"boat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A vessel
constructed for being towed, as a canal boat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A steamer used for towing other vessels; a
tug.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Towel</ent>⟦br⟧
